konachan:
Searches for an image on Konachan. Can only be used in NSFW channels. 

``x!konachan`` - Gets a random image from Konachan. 

``x!konachan [tag] [rating]`` - Gets an image with the specified tag and rating. You do need a tag if you wish to specify a rating.
danbooru: Searches for an image on Danbooru. Can only be used in NSFW channels.
